@chapter tinypokerd

@section Overview

@cindex tinypokerd
tinypokerd is the TinyPoker server. It will use
@cindex libtinypoker
libtinypoker to implement the
@cindex Internet Poker Protocol
Internet Poker Protocol (IPP). The code will be based on the pokerd
code base and experience implementing pokerd. An effort will be made
to make the server footprint even smaller than pokerd.

